<!-- Projects Section -->
<section class="projects" id="work">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-intro">
      <h2 class="text-reveal">Selected Work</h2>
      <p>Real businesses. Real builds. Real momentum.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="project-card">
    <div class="project-content">
      <span class="project-tag">Workflow & Ledger App</span>
      <h3>ARS Flows</h3>
      <p>Custom operating system designed to power a fast-moving <strong>equipment services operation</strong> supporting one of the world's most recognized brands. Technicians, admins, and the owner each get a <strong>purpose-built experience</strong> — four guided workflows with 19 steps that move jobs from intake through invoicing with <strong>full visibility at every stage</strong>. Built in <strong>9 weeks</strong> on React, TypeScript, and Supabase. Still humming.</p>
      <div class="stat-pills">
        <span class="stat-pill stat-pill--accent"><strong>4</strong> workflows, <strong>19</strong> guided steps</span>
        <span class="stat-pill"><strong>4</strong> role-based dashboards</span>
        <span class="stat-pill"><strong>6</strong>-phase job lifecycle</span>
        <span class="stat-pill"><strong>3</strong> distinct user roles</span>
        <span class="stat-pill"><strong>9</strong>-week initial build</span>
        <span class="stat-pill stat-pill--accent"><strong>Phase 2</strong> in progress</span>
      </div>
      <details class="project-expand project-expand--with-blog">
        <summary>
          <span class="project-expand-label">More about this project</span>
          <a href="/blog/build-the-blueprint/" class="project-blog-link" onclick="event.stopPropagation()">Read blog article →</a>
        </summary>
        <div class="project-expand-content">
          <p>One platform that gives every facility job a clear path — from the moment a work task is dispatched through final invoice. Phase 2 was blueprinted from real job data — <strong>12 process documents</strong> from an actual project were reverse-engineered into swim lane diagrams, a <strong>13-table data model</strong>, and screen-by-screen wireframes before a single line of code was written. The highest-value screen — a <strong>proposal builder</strong> with line-item management, auto-totals, and one-click PDF export — turns what used to take manual effort every time into something that flows in minutes.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
    <div class="project-gallery">
      <div class="project-gallery-track">
