      <span class="project-tag">Tech Training Platform</span>
      <h3>GMAC</h3>
      <p>Built for <strong>genuine mastery</strong> — the kind teams actually carry into the field. Two-sided training platform that turns dense technical knowledge into <strong>tablet-first microlearning</strong>, <strong>interactive 3D tools</strong>, and <strong>gamified quizzes</strong> frontline teams genuinely engage with. <strong>Role-based dashboards</strong> give managers clear visibility from <strong>individual performance up through store, district, area, and region</strong>.</p>
      <div class="stat-pills">
        <span class="stat-pill stat-pill--accent"><strong>50% → 96%</strong> knowledge scores</span>
        <span class="stat-pill"><strong>99%</strong> manager approval</span>
